{"tid":1257828,"cid":21,"subCid":8,"title":"【交流心得】挑選鋼琴 / 鋼琴整音","createTime":"2019-06-25T18:58:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T15:12:48.000Z","uid":269364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a7e556518fbdcc8b2db3f605f4925d45adc63bbb","tid":1257828,"uid":269364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:58:55.000Z","msg":"本身用緊Yamaha U3<br />\n未來目標想考埋FTCL，開始覺得U3有好多限制和不滿足佢個聲...為能夠更享受音樂帶黎嘅樂趣與快感，呢排開始睇唔同嘅鋼琴。<br />\n最好當然有部三角琴啦...但家裏實在冇位擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇過好多德國琴，好聽手感好的動輒20-30萬，暫時負擔唔起<br />\n1. 宜家考慮緊部yus5 (silent)，反應快，各方面比U3好，有埋靜音，全天候可以練琴...(雖然它的聲音比較冷，不是最喜愛的那種德國聲)<br />\n2. 第二個考慮方案，唔買琴住，同部U3做regulation+voicing先<br />\n希望有高人可以指點迷津，先感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"433b88f8e912f9de2b45b2284cce9eecc9f2c082","tid":1257828,"uid":144522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T04:41:19.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"e3cab899c32431d4ac5f6ca4f3c0bee7733f7875","tid":1257828,"uid":117709,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T18:48:34.000Z","msg":"你搵日去沙田講利，有部6萬幾嘅Boston，再比較隔離全新嘅11萬Boston、YUS5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6萬幾個部Boston，我一聽就知係正野，勁心動，可惜無能力買"},{"pid":"9ebe45c650d2a31225fa54b1709f6f482341087e","tid":1257828,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T18:48:44.000Z","msg":"通利"},{"pid":"bcc176fc546aa4fac7966627ae641c53b3ed6003","tid":1257828,"uid":269364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3cab899c32431d4ac5f6ca4f3c0bee7733f7875","tid":1257828,"uid":117709,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T18:48:34.000Z","msg":"你搵日去沙田講利，有部6萬幾嘅Boston，再比較隔離全新嘅11萬Boston、YUS5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6萬幾個部Boston，我一聽就知係正野，勁心動，可惜無能力買"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T14:25:48.000Z","msg":"謝謝巴打介紹！走咗轉沙田通利，可惜部Boston 131好似未調好音<im